CopyEvolutionEffectivity.Title: Copy
CopyEvolutionEffectivity.LongHelp: Copies the Evolution effectivity of an object so that you can paste it to another object in the structure.
CopyVariantEffectivity.Title: Copy
CopyVariantEffectivity.LongHelp: Copies the variant/option effectivity of an object so that you can paste it to another object in the structure.
EditEvolution.Title: Edit
EditEvolution.ShortHelp: Adds or edits the model version revisions that define evolution effectivity for an object in the structure.
EditEvolution.LongHelp: Opens the <wintitle>Edit Evolution</wintitle> dialog box for the object so that you can select which model version revisions define the object's evolution effectivity.
EditVariant.Title: Edit
EditVariant.ShortHelp: Adds or edits the variants and options effectivity for an object in the structure.
EditVariant.LongHelp: Opens the <wintitle>Define Variant/Option</wintitle> dialog box for the object so that you can add or edit variants and options to define the variants and options effectivity expression.
EvolutionMenu.Title: Evolution Effectivity
PasteEvolutionEffectivity.Title: Paste
PasteEvolutionEffectivity.LongHelp: Pastes the copied Evolution effectivity of one object on another object in the structure.
PasteVariantEffectivity.Title: Paste
PasteVariantEffectivity.LongHelp: Pastes the copied variant/option effectivity of one object on another object in the structure.
VariantOptionMenu.Title: Variant & Option
